data.description: Beautiful, Large, 4 Bedroom home situated on one of the largest lots in the neighborhood. Beautiful laminate floors throughout.  Carpeting in bedrooms. Large Living Room with Fireplace.  Spacious Family Room.  Kitchen with Corian countertops and desk area with Breakfast bar. Back Deck off of Kitchen. Nice Master Suite with walk-in closet. Laundry Room with Full size stackable washer/dryer and shelving. Smart Thermostat. Tankless Water Heater. Garage with its own A/C unit, storage racks above and shelving.  Lots of storage closets. Total energy efficient home.Low maintenance yard. PAID SOLAR. Refrigerator and Washer/Dryer convey. Across the street from Elementary and Middle Schools.  High School is close by also.
